# List of State Register of Heritage Places in the Shire of Broomehill-Tambellup

The State Register of Heritage Places is maintained by the Heritage Council of Western Australia. , 215 places are heritage-listed in the Shire of Broomehill-Tambellup, of which five are on the State Register of Heritage Places.
